### 📅 Monatlicher Netzbezug – Baseline vs. vermieden

{% set base = state_attr('sensor.e3dc_maestro_advisor_szenario', 'scenario_monthly_baseline_grid_in') or [] %}
{% set avoid = state_attr('sensor.e3dc_maestro_advisor_szenario', 'scenario_monthly_avoided_kwh') or [] %}
{% set months = ['Jan','Feb','Mär','Apr','Mai','Jun','Jul','Aug','Sep','Okt','Nov','Dez'] %}
{% set vmax = (base + avoid) | map('float', 0) | max if base else 0 %}
{% if base and vmax > 0 %}
| Monat | Baseline kWh | Vermieden kWh | Verteilung |
|-------|-------------:|--------------:|:-----------|
{% for i in range(12) -%}
{% set b = base[i] | float(0) %}
{% set a = avoid[i] | float(0) %}
{% set bw = (b / vmax * 20) | round(0, 'floor') | int %}
{% set aw = (a / vmax * 20) | round(0, 'floor') | int %}
| {{ months[i] }} | {{ b | round(0) }} | {{ a | round(0) }} | <span style="color:#e57373">{{ '█' * bw }}</span><span style="color:#66bb6a">{{ '█' * aw }}</span> |
{% endfor %}

<small>🟥 Baseline-Netzbezug · 🟩 vermiedener Netzbezug (Szenario)</small>
{% else %}
_Noch keine Szenario-Daten – bitte Analyse starten._
{% endif %}

