### 🏆 Top-Szenarien – Ersparnis vs. Investition

{% set top = state_attr('sensor.e3dc_maestro_advisor_sizing_matrix', 'top_savings_scenarios') or [] %}
{% if top %}
{% set smax = top | map(attribute='savings') | map('float', 0) | max %}
| +Akku/+PV | Ersparnis €/a | Invest € | Payback a | |
|-----------|--------------:|---------:|----------:|:--|
{% for r in top -%}
{% set s = r.savings | float(0) %}
{% set inv = r.invest | float(0) %}
{% set pay = (inv / s) if s > 0 else 0 %}
{% set sw = (s / smax * 15) | round(0, 'floor') | int if smax > 0 else 0 %}
| +{{ r.b }}/+{{ r.p }} | {{ s | round(0) }} | {{ inv | round(0) }} | {{ pay | round(1) }} | <span style="color:#66bb6a">{{ '█' * sw }}</span> |
{% endfor %}
{% else %}
_Noch keine Top-Szenarien – bitte Analyse starten._
{% endif %}
